outputs.output_descr: The project will support conservation and management of Eritrea's coastal, marine and island biodiversity through the establishment of biodiversity information system; increasing awareness of biodiversity values; development of an integrated coastal area management (ICAM) framework; conservation of special habitats and species through a netwerk of establishing marine Protected Areas (MPAs).
